          </a>
          <p>This project investigates the improper disposal of plastic waste, focusing on PET bottles, in Florianópolis and compares it with national and global data. Using real data, interactive graphs, and 3D visualizations, we aim to understand the problem's magnitude and propose solutions to reduce environmental impact.</p>
